paragraphs.title: Get the 10 most frequent words
paragraphs.text:
%flink
import org.apache.flink.util._
import scala.collection.mutable.PriorityQueue

val wordLength = 4
val numberOfWords = 5

val wordCountsFiltered = wordCounts.filter(x => x.word.length >= wordLength)
val result = getNMostFrequentWords(wordCountsFiltered, numberOfWords).collect()

paragraphs.title: Get top 10 Words without stop words
paragraphs.text:
%flink
import scala.collection.mutable.PriorityQueue

val numberOfWords = 10

val stopWordFiltered = wordCountsFiltered.filter{
    element => !stopWords.contains(element.word.toLowerCase)
}
val stopWordResult = getNMostFrequentWords(stopWordFiltered, numberOfWords).collect()
